  {
    q: 'What keywords do you target?',
    a: 'Problem-aware questions: "bricklayer for house", "brick wall cost", "brickwork contractor near me". Also location searches: "bricklayer KL".'
  },
  {
    q: 'Do I need 3 languages?',
    a: 'English dominates (95%), but Malay and Chinese help reach local contractors and developers. Expand your reach.'
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I see examples?',
    a: 'Yes. We show you exactly what keywords we\'ll target. You approve before we start. No surprises.'
  }
];
